node.text:
Congratulations to Mishie Chabba and Nerina Tosso for winning the Barked X Meowed VIP Club August new member rewards - USD$100 Amazon coupon!
Thank you Brandon Elvi for referring the most new members in August and you win a USD$100 Amazon coupon too!
.
🎁 Tap link in bio to join the “Barked X Meowed VIP Club” for FREE now!
.

-
